title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Dec 15 2021

description:
Senator Marsha Blackburn joins Clay and Buck to discuss "Build Back Broke" and the GOP chances in 2022. Psaki rightly stumped on question about Biden's biggest foreign policy achievement. Biden lies about Build Back Better, says it doesn't cost a penny. Two African-American intellectuals who say America is not a racist country.
